title: Bobby Worried He’s Been Scammed + Famous First Lines Of Country Songs + Raymundo’s Surrogate Situation Update
itunes:title: Bobby Worried He’s Been Scammed + Famous First Lines Of Country Songs + Raymundo’s Surrogate Situation Update
description:
Bobby is now worried that he may have been scammed this week by a guy claiming to be from the census. We play a game where the show has to guess the 2000’s country songs based on the famous first lines of their lyrics. Plus, we get an update from Raymundo on his sister being his surrogate!
